snippet: Top-seeded Gaël Monfils beat Jarkko Nieminen, 7-5, 3-6, 6-2, in the Stockholm Open final for his first title of the year.
lead_paragraph: Top-seeded Gaël Monfils beat Jarkko Nieminen, 7-5, 3-6, 6-2, in the Stockholm Open final for his first title of the year.
